videos.description: Eric Bledsoe drives and floats up a lob pass for Jaxson Hayes to rise up and flush down with two hands for a Pelicans dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bledsoe lobs to Hayes for Pelicans dunk) 2021/01/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bledsoe lobs to Hayes for Pelicans dunk

videos.description: Myles Turner knocks down a clutch 3-pointer to tie the game for the Pacers, and Brandon Ingram comes up with a big block for New Orleans on the next possession to force overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Turner hits big 3, Ingram gets the block to force OT) 2021/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Turner hits big 3, Ingram gets the block to force OT

videos.description: Zion Williamson records a double-double of 24 points and 10 assists, but the Pelicans fall short as they lose 118-116 in overtime to the Pacers.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Zion's double-double not enough to take down Pacers) 2021/01/04 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion's double-double not enough to take down Pacers
